epoque.name: EPOQUE
epoque.description:
Your past, your future, your EPOQUE.
The EPOQUE line arose from the serendipitous and unintended actions of fashion designers, and has gradually become a tradition among designers over hundreds of years. This not-for-profit, pure, and calm-minded approach to fashion design will become a tenet for every era.

nian.name: Made by 0011
nian.description:
Established Year 0011.
In order to celebrate the victory over the Nian beast, artisans craft clothes each year for soldiers in the image and colors of the Nian beast. Year after year follows, with festivities and celebrations roaring like firecrackers.

whirlwind.name: 0011/Tempest
whirlwind.description:
New Year, New Trends.
0011's sub-brand, 'Tempest,' focuses on capturing the sights and sounds of the streets. This series is rooted in the inspired and constantly-shifting styles of the streets, transforming the latest and trendiest ideas into a revolutionary new look.

yun.name: 0011/Yun
yun.description:
Lingering Essence
0011 Yun Series looks back on the city's past, drawing upon the beauty of old times. The Yun series reshapes fashion with classic essence, sterling craftsmanship, and unique innovation, expanding the frontiers of the future through the past.

summer.name: Coral Coast
summer.description:
Show your true self!
Coral Coast is a sub-brand of MARTHE, mainly for water sports and summer attire, imbuing fashion with the vitality of summer. Inheriting MARTHE's philosophy, this series focuses on bringing cutting-edge design to fit the needs of the wearer, and embellishing the coastline with beautiful colors year after year.

marthe.name: MARTHE
marthe.description:
Go all out.
A famous sports fashion brand with a renowned Kazdel designer. This brand has gained popularity in the sportswear market throughout many countries, and particularly loved in Ursus. It has many sub-brands, which intimately cater to the complex needs of its customers.

witch.name: Witch Feast
witch.description:
The night approaches, and the Witch Feast is nigh.
Rhodes Island holds its Witch Feast festivities every year, turning an ancient tradition long restricted to female Sarkaz into something everyone can enjoy. During the merriment, colorful costumes and decorations can be seen all over, and these festive outfits are sure to become a fond memory for all the operators.

winter.name: Cambrian Series
winter.description:
Do not fear the cold.
The Cambrian brand is known for its cold-protection properties. Well received in the colder regions of Terra, Cambrian gradually expanded outwards with the advent of greater climate change. One of the original brands for messengers, Cambrian continues to introduce new products but holds onto the same core ideal - providing safety, warmth, and elegance.

xmas.name: Icefield Messenger
xmas.description:
He giveth, yet asketh for nothing in return.
Since ancient times, the legend of a messenger has circulated across Terra. Wearing a red outfit and riding a sleigh, he crossed the vast snowy tundra to deliver life-saving supplies to others. To commemorate this messenger, his story has become a brand, carrying people's simple and pure wishes.

wild.name: Vitafield
wild.description:
Life, Unbound.
The Vitafield line focuses on the design of outdoor attire. We heard our customers' desire for exploring the world around them, and delivered with our lightweight, durable, and exceptionally-designed products. After finishing the first production run, Vitafield became a novel trend even among the general public.

sweep.name: Raythean Pioneer
sweep.description:
Pioneer, explore the unknown.
The Pioneer series is a subdivision of Raythean, dedicated to providing new possibilities for professionals. The Pioneer series fills the niche of a clothing market suited for professionals who work in extreme environments. Emphasizing reliability, ease of use, and easy maintenance, allow us to accompany you as you pioneer uncharted territory.

boc.name: Bloodline of Combat
boc.description:
Through the bloodline, the struggle continues.
'Bloodline of Combat' is an experimental personal equipment series developed by Rhodes Island in collaboration with other organizations based upon the actual needs of operators. The equipment is densely packed with advanced, and potentially even dangerous technology, for operators to be able to deal with the most demanding tasks. Rhodes Island and its operators never give up.

kitchen.name: Rhodes Kitchen
kitchen.description:
Fine clothes, fine flavors, and a fine future.
Rhodes Island operators hail from every corner of Terra, and bring with them their own cuisine from home. The festive attire of the Rhodes Kitchen series originate from a combination of food culture and the operators' feedback, brought to life with the artistry of the designer operators.

ghost.name: Dreambind Castle
ghost.description:
Your terrorbound slumber. Face your fears.
Once again, Pathyell Castle has been shrouded in mist. Dreams torment the people, while wicked spirits run the streets amok. The Viscount of the Final Age, who set these affairs in motion, now lies dormant far beneath the castle grounds. The Operative Investigators are called to settle the matter—they must delve deep into the Castle, and unearth its truest secrets held within.

race.name: Whistlewind
race.description:
Cheers for racing!!!
The Whistlewind brand boasts a depth of years tied to the clothing of Victoria's motor races. With mature design experience and assembly pipelines, ensuring aesthetics as a first principle, conducting rigorous checks on material quality, its sole goal is to offer the most intimate support to the race queens and drivers as they ascend the podium, world watching.

striker.name: Raythean Striker
striker.description:
Striker, valiantly step forward.
The Striker series is a subdivision of Raythean, dedicated to providing equipment support to professional specialist units. The Striker series gives all-round consideration to a breadth of scenarios involving specialist combat, employing on-site tests to ensure product performance. Allow us to accompany you as you strike forth, prevail, and press onward.

ambienceSynesthesia.name: Ambience Synesthesia
ambienceSynesthesia.description:
Heart with the rhythm, give it up to the rock.
Every concert embodies its hosts' beating blood, and preparing performers' outfits with that in mind is the one and only mission of the Ambience Synesthesia brand. No matter whether formal or streetwear, we'll stop at no end to provide musicians the most fitting attire for when the lights go on.

crossover.name: Collab Series
crossover.description:
Together we stand.
Rhodes Island cooperates with other organizations to launch these fashion lines. These mutually beneficial cooperation agreements create a win-win situation, and operators even get to enjoy some fresh attire.

shining.name: Shining Steps
shining.description:
Step up, all eyes on you!
Monster Siren Records' exclusive idol project clothing brand invites big-name designers to dedicate themselves to the art of stage costumes for young people with idol dreams. The time is now, step up to the ladder and climb the rungs to be the idol only you can be!

game.name: Achievement Star
game.description:
Press Start
Casual clothing made for gamers, comfortable while maximizing the gaming experience.

iteration.name: Iteration Provident
iteration.description:
Two Paths, One Goal
So-called 'fate' has been recursive from the start, a harmonious reconstruction, a mirror with limitless reflections. And then came you.

unveiling.name: Unveiling of Devotion
unveiling.description:
It's what everyone's been waiting for! Słoma brazenly advances into all-new territory!
Bringing together the best and brightest of Kazimierz's creative talent, for a limited time only, while supplies last! Love won't announce itself, so muster up your courage, brush off your shyness, and seize your treasure with your own hands!

char_002_amiya_winter#1.name: Newsgirl
char_002_amiya_winter#1.description:
LIMITED EDITION
Test Collection/Newsgirl. Available only in certain regions, this remake of a classic design utilizes the best materials and contains carefully-sewn details. An extra custom-made letter opener is included.

char_181_flower_daily#1.name: Species Plantarum
char_181_flower_daily#1.description: Test Collection/Species Plantarum. Available only in certain regions, this remake of a classic design utilizes the best materials carefully hand-sewn details. An extra custom-made multifunctional tool bag is included.

char_002_amiya_epoque#4.name: Fresh Fastener
char_002_amiya_epoque#4.description: Test Collection Series/Fresh Fastener. An outfit worn by Amiya while working for a Rhodes Island restaurant. This poofy coat is cold-resistant, and has enough room to hold something penguin-sized.

char_002_amiya_test#1.name: Seedsower
char_002_amiya_test#1.description: Test Collection Series/Seedsower. A loose yet comfortable outdoors fit. Comes with an exclusive miniature mountain-grade rucksack and an agricultural nursery kit. The designer has one small wish of her own, and hopes that we can all help to realize it.

char_202_demkni_test#1.name: The Law
char_202_demkni_test#1.description: Test Collection Series/The Law. The jailer garments Saria used when entering Mansfield State Prison, largely in line with the female jailer's standard uniform.

char_250_phatom_sale#4.name: Focus
char_250_phatom_sale#4.description: Test Collection Series/Focus. The attire Phantom wore when he left for the castle, and the costume for his maiden performance. After an age of gathering dust, it finally sees the light of day again.

char_211_adnach_sale#5.name: Traceless Walker
char_211_adnach_sale#5.description: Test Collection Series/Traceless Walker. Custom-made by the Lateran Curia for certain Legati. Sankta who get custom outfits all share a common feature: there is something unusual about their halos.

char_210_stward_sale#6.name: Snowstorm Invitation
char_210_stward_sale#6.description: Test Collection Series/Snowstorm Invitation. An outfit tailor-made by Karlan Trade for their affiliated business negotiators. First impressions are of the utmost importance in trade talks. Steward knows this well, and has never failed to live up to expectations.

char_437_mizuki_sale#7.name: Summer Feast
char_437_mizuki_sale#7.description: Test Collection Series/Summer Feast. Mizuki wears this when feasting on the beach. The material is stain-resistant and provides plenty of room for extra appendages.

char_103_angel_sale#8.name: Midnight Delivery
char_103_angel_sale#8.description: Test Collection Series/Midnight Delivery. As part of our cooperation agreement, Rhodes Island ordered this operator uniform for Exusiai. She can be seen wearing it, from time to time, during operations in Lungmen.

char_362_saga_sale#9.name: There They Be
char_362_saga_sale#9.description: Test Collection Series/There They Be. Saga's attire when she left P'o-shan Village, with Biteys for pockets and straw sandals. What is in the scrolls cannot be removed, but after so much time spent with oneselves, what was drawn in ink is now etched in the heart.

char_010_chen_sale#10.name: After Storm
char_010_chen_sale#10.description: Test Collection Series/After Storm. Frost inevitably gives way to a clear day. Ch'en Hui-chieh patrols the city in her first L.G.D. uniform, re-inspecting the metropolis both familiar and foreign to her.

char_208_melan_epoque#1.name: Letters from Wessex
char_208_melan_epoque#1.description: A uniform from Victoria's Wessex Middle School, adapted by traditional Victorian designers. Centuries of rich heritage combines with excellent craftsmanship to make a light and comfortable outfit.

char_109_fmout_epoque#2.name: Unknown Journey
char_109_fmout_epoque#2.description: EPOQUE New Arrivals/Unknown Journey. Trendy, made for the spring season, well-fitting and comfortable, comes with a choice of accessories that can be mixed and matched to suit your style.

char_187_ccheal_epoque#2.name: Combat Medic
char_187_ccheal_epoque#2.description: EPOQUE First Edition/Combat Medic. Based upon a special-issue Ádakrys battlesuit, it has blades attached in the right parts to give off an extremely aggressive look. Gavial describes it as her ideal 'battlefield trappings.'

char_128_plosis_epoque#3.name: Serenity
char_128_plosis_epoque#3.description: EPOQUE New Arrivals/Serenity. Casual clothing centered around black and purple as main colors to exude a bit of elegance while still maintaining a calm feel. A favorite among women in the workplace, this outfit was Ptilopsis's first choice when going out.

char_215_mantic_epoque#4.name: Invisible Dirge
char_215_mantic_epoque#4.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Invisible Dirge. Taking the model's peculiar traits in consideration, this outfit was completed without being tailored. Combines comfort, fashion, and a proper fit while also protecting the operator's vitals.

char_164_nightm_epoque#5.name: Light and Shadow
char_164_nightm_epoque#5.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Light and Shadow. A trendy, vintage Victorian appeal, modified to Nightmare's specifications. Some decorative elements will change when Nightmare's personality shifts.

char_213_mostma_epoque#5.name: Spellbreaker
char_213_mostma_epoque#5.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Spellbreaker. A Laterano dress with corresponding weapons. Generally, only Sankta who have presided over the ceremonies are allowed to wear it, and Mostima seems to have quietly snuck out with this outfit.

char_274_astesi_epoque#5.name: Starseeker
char_274_astesi_epoque#5.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Starseeker. One of the intricate outfits worn by Astesia only in the grandest occasions of Columbia's social life. Merely donning this outfit is a statement of its own.

char_220_grani_epoque#6.name: Miraculous Moment
char_220_grani_epoque#6.description: EPOQUE New Series/Miraculous Moment. Casual clothes that capture the region's impressions while taking the customer's preferences in consideration. After a deep dive into the customer's life, the designer collaborated with the customer to add a variety of supporting accessories.

char_113_cqbw_epoque#7.name: Fugue
char_113_cqbw_epoque#7.description: EPOQUE Line [Passe] Series Selects/Fugue. Ordinary Sarkaz mercenary wear. Easy to mend, protective, and carries even more explosives after simple modification.

char_102_texas_epoque#7.name: Willpower
char_102_texas_epoque#7.description: EPOQUE Line [Passe] Series Selects/Willpower. Classic Siracusan womenswear. By request of Texas, all parts once white have been dyed completely black.

char_130_doberm_epoque#7.name: Lieutenant
char_130_doberm_epoque#7.description: EPOQUE Line [Passe] Series Selects/Lieutenant. Clothing modified from Bolívarian military uniform, with some accessories coming from Dobermann's own collection.

char_355_ethan_epoque#7.name: Infiltrator
char_355_ethan_epoque#7.description: EPOQUE Line [Passe] Series Selects/Infiltrator. This clothing is styled exactly as Ethan used to wear, but closer-fitting, cozier, making him somewhat unwilling to change out of it.

char_253_greyy_epoque#8.name: Eggcellent Craftsman
char_253_greyy_epoque#8.description: EPOQUE New Arrivals/Eggcellent Craftsman. Greyy made an exquisite eight-tone musical egg as a present for his close friends, and in exchange, they custom-ordered him this outfit brimming with holiday atmosphere.

char_344_beewax_epoque#9.name: Weißer Sand
char_344_beewax_epoque#9.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Weißer Sand. Home leisure style, a present from Carnelian to Beeswax. She believed this one would fit her most, and knew Beeswax would like it.

char_343_tknogi_epoque#9.name: Londinium Style Miko
char_343_tknogi_epoque#9.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Londinium Style Miko. Home leisure style, standard apparel for Victorian housekeeping staff. The pattern on the skirt hem was embroidered in improvisation by Tsukinogi, who seems to have misunderstood this clothing's use case.

char_181_flower_epoque#9.name: Leisurely Afternoon
char_181_flower_epoque#9.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Leisurely Afternoon. Home leisure style, relaxed and pleasing to the eye, graceful and cozy. Comes with a pair of adorable fitted slippers, for an afternoon completely free of cares wherever you are.

char_258_podego_epoque#9.name: Wake Up From a Nap
char_258_podego_epoque#9.imgAlt: Podenco's "Wake Up From a Nap" skin
char_258_podego_epoque#9.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Wake Up From a Nap. Home leisure style, selected for Podenco by Lena. Similar colors to Podenco's original clothing, but with a complete change of style.

char_126_shotst_epoque#10.name: Bard's Holiday
char_126_shotst_epoque#10.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Bard's Holiday. Trendy autumn attire, loose and breathable. Incorporates a unique multi-layer pocket design, convenient for holding all sorts of lightweight souvenirs during a serendipitous sojourn.

char_265_sophia_epoque#11.name: Glory Purple
char_265_sophia_epoque#11.description: EPOQUE Line [Passe] Series Selects/Glory Purple. Zofia's attire when she participated in the Kazimierz Major awards ceremony. The right choice of attire made her the center of attention during the ceremony.

char_151_myrtle_epoque#12.name: Light Gold Celebration
char_151_myrtle_epoque#12.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Light Gold Celebration. Generalissimo Myrtle's attire during her triumphant return. Stand at attention—— and salute!

char_485_pallas_epoque#12.name: Heritage
char_485_pallas_epoque#12.description: EPOQUE Line [Passe] Series Selects/Heritage. Traditional Minoan ritual attire, coordinated with modern themes, is once again in vogue among Minoans.

char_197_poca_epoque#12.name: Masterpiece
char_197_poca_epoque#12.description: EPOQUE Line [Passe] Series Selects/Masterpiece. The outfit worn by Natalya Andreyevna Rostova, student council president of Chernobog #4 Secondary School, during her commencement speech.

char_218_cuttle_epoque#12.name: Silent Arrow
char_218_cuttle_epoque#12.description: EPOQUE Line [Passe] Series Selects/Silent Arrow. An Iberian classic, enhanced with the customer's own artistic touches. Andreana particularly appreciates this outfit's moisture resistance.

char_451_robin_epoque#13.name: Gift of Wild
char_451_robin_epoque#13.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Gift of Wild. The choice of the Columbian pioneer, with a core emphasis on strong and durable design. The added details give this outfit that extra personal touch.

char_479_sleach_epoque#14.name: Appreciate Fragrance
char_479_sleach_epoque#14.description: EPOQUE Series New Release/Appreciate Fragrance. Finely-crafted Victorian dress, handmade from the finest materials. An elegant and dignified outfit bound to garner attention anywhere.

char_473_mberry_epoque#14.name: Plant Crude Drug
char_473_mberry_epoque#14.description: EPOQUE Series New Release/Plant Crude Drug. Practical outfit worn by Mulberry for both relief and horticultural work, with enough pockets for all her tools. Green trimmings adorn the simple fabric, representing verdant life.

char_2024_chyue_nian#10.name: Alighting
char_2024_chyue_nian#10.description: 0011 Custom Brand [Magnificence Curation] Series Collection/Alighting. Magnum opus of a Yumen craftsman, given to a traveler heading on a long journey. In the hope that men and might need no longer be a burden, that he can wander for myriad li with ease.

char_4080_lin_nian#10.name: Heavenly Mirage
char_4080_lin_nian#10.description: 0011 Custom Brand [Magnificence Curation] Series Collection/Heavenly Mirage. Recreation of a Lungmen VIP's childhood fantasy. She enters the Xians' abode, dressed in celestial garb, skirts dark as kohl, jade pure as ice, face austere, serene. Transcendent.

char_4066_highmo_nian#10.name: The Land With Me
char_4066_highmo_nian#10.description: 0011 Custom Brand [Magnificence Curation] Series Collection/The Land With Me. Handmade by a Lungmen craftsman, inspired by Yanese landscape paintings. Thanks to weaving and dyeing techniques rarely seen in the modern age, mounts and seas emerge from the nichang's fabric, blurring fantasy and reality.

char_449_glider_nian#10.name: Saturated Within Rain
char_449_glider_nian#10.description: 0011 Custom Brand [Magnificence Curation] Series Collection/Saturated Within Rain. Handmade by a Lungmen craftsman, matching a scene of beauty and wonder recorded in an ancient tome. Remember to bring a paper umbrella, for within, the drops of ink now fall as gentle rains.

char_385_finlpp_nian#11.name: Yearly Present
char_385_finlpp_nian#11.description: 0011 New Arrivals/Yearly Present. Purestream dons new clothes and brings a gift for her visit, the trendy multi-layered style unable to hide the bright colors of Yan—the hem's red lining and the pendants on her staff and her waist come together in harmonious ingenuity.

char_402_tuye_epoque#14.name: Cultivate Vegetation
char_402_tuye_epoque#14.description: EPOQUE Series New Release/Cultivate Vegetation. Rugged traditional Sargon outfit, suitable for long journeys. The new collar details give the wearer a closer fit.

char_337_utage_epoque#15.name: Disguise
char_337_utage_epoque#15.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Disguise. Home leisure style, snug and cozy material. Dark purple and tangerine yellow collide for a full-on sense of vogue.

char_264_f12yin_epoque#15.name: Book Reader
char_264_f12yin_epoque#15.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Book Reader. Traditional Victorian textiles and tailoring, every cut made by the hands of craftsmen, its custom-made monochrome cloth premium without being conspicuous.

char_475_akafyu_epoque#15.name: Temperament
char_475_akafyu_epoque#15.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Temperament. Adroit tailoring and a rich modern sense for color, contrasted with accessories detailed with classical appeal. Spectacles are custom-made as a gift by the brand, for the client.

char_496_wildmn_epoque#16.name: Justice Maker
char_496_wildmn_epoque#16.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Justice Maker. Attire of Wild Mane during repairs of 'Justice Knight.' Cozy and breathable, while wear and stain resistant. Detailing and accessories in contrasting colors coordinated to embody that sense of planning.

char_472_pasngr_epoque#17.name: Dream In A Moment
char_472_pasngr_epoque#17.description: EPOQUE Sub-Brand [Passe] Series Selects/Dream In A Moment. Two sets of clothing held in Passenger's memories and casually put to paper, then realized as outfits by a snooping Operator.

char_1014_nearl2_epoque#17.name: Relight
char_1014_nearl2_epoque#17.description: EPOQUE Sub-Brand [Passe] Series Selects/Relight. One of the many suits of armor worn by Nearl in her debut competition season, this one a modification of a campaign knight suit.

char_391_rosmon_epoque#17.name: Become Anew
char_391_rosmon_epoque#17.description: EPOQUE Sub-Brand [Passe] Series Selects/Become Anew. Rosmontis's attire while still a test subject, adorned only by detectors and inhibitors.

char_449_glider_epoque#17.name: Wildness Behind
char_449_glider_epoque#17.description: EPOQUE Sub-Brand [Passe] Series Selects/Wildness Behind. The clothes Honeyberry envisioned during her studies as she described her own prospects to her sickly mother, their intricacies drawn from her mother's wardrobe.

char_101_sora_epoque#17.name: Melodiosa
char_101_sora_epoque#17.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Melodiosa. Sora's outfit in her time studying and performing at Siracusa's Teatro di Milano. Siracusan musical productions have a unique cultural flair, which in turn calls for accessorizing to match.

char_492_quercu_epoque#17.name: Distant Home's Guide
char_492_quercu_epoque#17.description: EPOQUE Sub-Brand [Passe] Series Selects/Distant Home's Guide. The plainclothes Quercus once wore on an infiltration mission. Principally serving to conceal her identity, so as to better facilitate combat in city environs.

char_4013_kjera_epoque#18.name: Ingenious Servant
char_4013_kjera_epoque#18.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Ingenious Servant. A bespoke outfit ordered at the Savile Boutique Tailors by Kjera, the finished product of bewildering quality thanks to the fantastic minds of the designers, plus Kjera's own clever touch.

char_485_pallas_epoque#19.name: A Drip of Orea and Potamous
char_485_pallas_epoque#19.imgAlt: Pallas's "A Drip of Orea and Potamous" skin
char_485_pallas_epoque#19.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/A Drip of Orea and Potamous. Designed for the climate of Minos, slim-fitting and easy to move in. The fabric is durable, waterproof, and resistant to the occasional spilled wine. Can be customized with extras to the customer's needs.

char_215_mantic_epoque#19.name: Under A Veil
char_215_mantic_epoque#19.description: EPOQUE Sub-Brand [Passe] Series Selects/Under A Veil. Manticore once wore it on a mission in Sargon, and was bothered by the clanging of the gold accessories as she moved.

char_4036_forcer_epoque#20.name: Paper Wing
char_4036_forcer_epoque#20.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Paper Wing. White jacket on mint-green T-shirt, refreshingly cool for the summer.

char_358_lisa_epoque#22.name: Yukibare
char_358_lisa_epoque#22.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Yukibare. Suzuran's outfit on a winter morning trip to the shrine. The loose-fitting sleeves protect against the wind and snow, while the pleated front adds an exotic touch.

char_388_mint_epoque#22.name: Tsukiyoi
char_388_mint_epoque#22.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Tsukiyoi. Custom-made for Mint, integrating Victorian style into traditional Higashinese garb. Comfy yet unique, it is one of Mint's favorites on festive occasions.

char_336_folivo_epoque#22.name: Betsushi
char_336_folivo_epoque#22.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Betsushi. Traditional Higashinese outfit made from the highest-quality fabric, colorful yet minimalistic. Comfortable and warm, an ideal choice for outdoor trips in autumn.

char_274_astesi_epoque#23.name: Fantastic Crafts
char_274_astesi_epoque#23.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Fantastic Crafts. Astesia and her sister wore this for a machine design competition. Lightweight, durable, and easy to clean, a stylish outfit for a hard-worker.

char_4039_horn_epoque#24.name: To Effloresce Whitely
char_4039_horn_epoque#24.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/To Effloresce Whitely. A gown for Victorian nobles woven with fine muslin, fragrant and supple flowers gracing the pure white skirt. A quiet elegance, delicate and sublime.

char_4045_heidi_epoque#24.name: A Thousand Correspondences
char_4045_heidi_epoque#24.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/A Thousand Correspondences. A custom outfit made of fine and lightweight material, tailored based on Heidi's descriptions of her childhood summers. Though it feels different from how she remembers.

char_297_hamoni_epoque#24.name: Invitation
char_297_hamoni_epoque#24.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Invitation. A set of formalwear Harmonie wears while enjoying the afternoon in her study. The smart tailoring makes her skirt move in a beautiful curve, and the fabrics are specially chosen to hide any stray fur stuck on her clothes.

char_135_halo_epoque#25.name: Her Aspiration
char_135_halo_epoque#25.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Her Aspiration. The clothes Astgenne wore in her rented home. A lab coat thrown over an elegant and close fit, for she must always be ready for a whimsical stroke of inspiration for her experiments.

char_209_ardign_epoque#26.name: Sunny Day
char_209_ardign_epoque#26.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Sunny Day. Cardigan's outfit when she had just arrived at a city in southern Leithanien. Skillfully tailored to fit a young girl's stature. Light, airy, and blooming with vitality.

token_10028_vigil_wolf_epoque#27.name: The Other Side of Siracusa
token_10028_vigil_wolf_epoque#27.imgAlt: Wolfpack's "The Other Side of Siracusa" skin

char_427_vigil_epoque#27.name: The Other Side of Siracusa
char_427_vigil_epoque#27.imgAlt: Vigil's "The Other Side of Siracusa" skin
char_427_vigil_epoque#27.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/The Other Side of Siracusa. Does he not occasionally wear a plain jacket and hoodie instead of a tailored suit, and sit-down at a not-quite traditional Siracusan restaurant?

char_126_shotst_epoque#28.name: Gwiazdcytrony
char_126_shotst_epoque#28.description: EPOQUE Sub-Brand [Passe] Series Selects/Gwiazdcytrony. Meteor's winter clothes from back in Kazimierz. Balancing lightness and warmth, they also allow one to easily hide in dense forests. A reproduction.

char_4064_mlynar_epoque#28.name: W Dali
char_4064_mlynar_epoque#28.description: EPOQUE Sub-Brand [Passe] Series Selects/W Dali. Młynar's attire as a knight-errant, wandering Kazimierz's plains and endless forests, the words engraved on the hilt of his sword not yet covered by useless trinkets.

char_222_bpipe_epoque#28.name: Royal Guardswoman
char_222_bpipe_epoque#28.description: EPOQUE Sub-Brand [Passe] Series Selects/Royal Guardswoman. Bagpipe's uniform as a new cadet at the military academy, doubling as formal wear. Training in formal wear was yet another duty of a royal guardsman cadet.

char_405_absin_epoque#28.name: Noon Twilight
char_405_absin_epoque#28.description: EPOQUE Sub-Brand [Passe] Series Selects/Noon Twilight. Absinthe's former school uniform. In Ursus, students wear their uniforms while exercising, resembling a field of neatly spaced seedlings behind a plow.

char_431_ashlok_epoque#28.name: Lances of Kaliskas
char_431_ashlok_epoque#28.description: EPOQUE Sub-Brand [Passe] Series Selects/Lances of Kaliskas. Ashlock's formalwear, worn when her family banished her. Traditional dress worthy of a Kazimierz knight, not entirely inappropriate on her.

char_4017_puzzle_epoque#29.name: Amidst the Pieces
char_4017_puzzle_epoque#29.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Amidst the Pieces. Puzzle knows that he should tailor his attire to his target—one of the most efficient ways to win trust and exchange intel. When alone, however, he barely spares a thought to his appearance.

char_212_ansel_epoque#29.name: Nighttime Café
char_212_ansel_epoque#29.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Nighttime Café. Always meticulous, Ansel likes to be properly dressed at the café as well. He steadfastly refuses to sell coffee at night, however.

char_1020_reed2_epoque#30.name: Curator
char_1020_reed2_epoque#30.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Curator. Scholar's garb straight from a fairy tale. Stuff your magic, knowledge, and curiosity in the pockets, and take notes with Reed.

char_388_mint_epoque#30.name: Private Study
char_388_mint_epoque#30.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Private Study. Mint's formalwear at the Victorian Institution for Higher Studies, the green waistband showing off her lines and individuality.

char_183_skgoat_epoque#30.name: Major Field
char_183_skgoat_epoque#30.description: EPOQUE Collection New Arrivals/Major Field. Practical yet dignified, it protects from the elements on field surveys, but can also be worn under a jacket for conferences.

char_120_hibisc_nian#1.name: Night Watcher
char_120_hibisc_nian#1.description: 0011 New Arrivals/Night Watcher. Handmade by Lungmen craftsman, this stylish outfit combines comfortable materials with cutting-edge tech and traditional handicraft. Custom-made services are also available. Fireproof.

char_010_chen_nian#2.name: Ageless Afterglow
char_010_chen_nian#2.description: 0011 New Arrivals/Ageless Afterglow. Handcrafted by Lungmen artisans, this tailor-made dress is comfortable, beautiful, and accentuates one's figure. By popular request, it has been made to be a bit sportier than the standard line.

char_308_swire_nian#2.name: Honor and Splendor
char_308_swire_nian#2.description: 0011 New Arrivals/Honor and Splendor. Handcrafted by Lungmen artisans, this outfit synergizes a wide variety of practical fabrics, providing a truly holistic look to meet exacting demands while still maintaining an affordable price.

char_107_liskam_nian#2.name: Spring Vouivre
char_107_liskam_nian#2.description: 0011 New Arrivals/Spring Vouivre. Completely handmade by Lungmen craftsman, this stylish outfit combines comfortable materials with cutting-edge tech and traditional handicraft. Custom-made services are also provided in order to achieve the highest practicability and style.

char_235_jesica_nian#2.name: Clivia
char_235_jesica_nian#2.description: 0011 New Arrivals/Clivia. Handmade by Lungmen craftsman, this outfit enjoys several benefits from its high-tech materials: light weight, breathability and durability. Furthermore, its waterproof fabric possesses high thermal performance, making it practical and exquisite at the same time. Limited edition.

char_136_hsguma_nian#3.name: Ronin Huntress
char_136_hsguma_nian#3.description: 0011 Tempest-Series New Arrival/Patrolling Ronin. Several designers joined forces to create a look inspired by the style of the streets. Complete with the redesigned shield of an L.G.D. Officer joined with traditional elements from Higashi, this outfit brings a truly formidable look.

char_2014_nian_nian#4.name: Unfettered Freedom
char_2014_nian_nian#4.description: 0011 New Arrivals/Unfettered Freedom. Handcrafted by Lungmen artisans, per the client's requests, twenty-four different designs of traditional women's clothing were drawn up, from which the client rolled dice to select one to ultimately be made into an outfit.

char_225_haak_nian#4.name: Doctor of Faces
char_225_haak_nian#4.description: 0011 New Arrivals/Doctor of Faces. Handcrafted by Lungmen artisans, with a design concept more inclined towards the East, its main appeal is to highlight the wearer's personality. Onlookers can sense the simplicities and trends of Lungmen.

char_226_hmau_nian#4.name: Just A Driver
char_226_hmau_nian#4.description: 0011 New Arrivals/Just A Driver. Handcrafted by Lungmen artisans, with a design concept more inclined towards the West, its main appeal being to create a balanced sense of uniform. Many fasteners adorn the outfit, reserving space for the client to personalize, mix and match.

char_436_whispr_nian#4.name: Tremble Cold
char_436_whispr_nian#4.description: 0011 New Arrivals/Tremble Cold. Handcrafted by Lungmen artisans, the typical clothing assembly process was refined in accordance with Ægir bodily characteristics, and the outfit displays a uniquely streamlined effect in turn. Color choices are made independently by the client.

char_225_haak_nian#5.name: Healing Hand, Evil Heart
char_225_haak_nian#5.description: 0011 New Arrivals/Healing Hand, Evil Heart. Handmade in Lungmen, the outfit includes multiple pieces of clothing that can be mixed and matched based on the customer's mood. The details in the outfit have been adjusted according to his needs, and includes an old-fashioned medicine box.

char_1011_lava2_nian#6.name: Dusk Wisteria
char_1011_lava2_nian#6.description: 0011 New Release / Dusk Wisteria. Handmade in Lungmen, tailor-fitted with special consideration to exotic design elements. The outfit has been improved in accordance with the customer's preference to incorporate Yan's novel trends.

char_2015_dusk_nian#7.name: Everything Is a Miracle
char_2015_dusk_nian#7.description: 0011 New Release / Everything Is a Miracle. A silky and delicate satin surface, perfectly fitted to the wearer's body shape. Blue-green envelops the body, invoking an ancient charm. After completing the outfit's design, the client draws it into existence, ready-to-wear, with a stroke of the brush.

char_455_nothin_nian#7.name: Pale Rising Moon
char_455_nothin_nian#7.description: 0011 New Release / Pale Rising Moon. Inspired by the outfits Mr. Nothing uses to conceal others, with an improved design. Just as the moon waxes and wanes, some people occasionally decide to break character and act debonair.

char_241_panda_nian#7.name: Gourmet
char_241_panda_nian#7.description: 0011 New Release / Gourmet. FEater's outfit from a bestselling Lungmen foodie film. Incorporates a sporty inner layer and a traditional knotted jacked, once all the rage.

char_469_indigo_nian#7.name: Serene Day
char_469_indigo_nian#7.description: 0011 New Release / Serene Day. Handmade in Lungmen. The fabric is light and comfortable, using the client's favorite purple color as a base and embellished with dark lines. Casual yet dignified, it is perfect for all sorts of occasions.

char_1021_kroos2_nian#8.name: Along the Corridor
char_1021_kroos2_nian#8.imgAlt: Kroos the Keen Glint's "Along the Corridor" skin
char_1021_kroos2_nian#8.description: 0011 New Arrivals/Along the Corridor. Made by Lungmen craftsmen from premium Shangshu silk. Elegant and classical patterns with cyan lining make for a dignified outfit.

char_476_blkngt_nian#8.name: Fragrance From the Branches
char_476_blkngt_nian#8.description: 0011 New Arrivals/Fragrance From the Branches. Clean-cut, form-fitting skirt, given an extra touch with matching accessories. The soft felt jacket keeps the wearer warm in the chill of early spring.

char_2023_ling_nian#9.name: It Does Wash the Strings
char_2023_ling_nian#9.imgAlt: Ling's "It Does Wash the Strings" skin
char_2023_ling_nian#9.description: 0011 New Arrivals/It Does Wash the Strings. Robe made from white cloth, with loose-fitting sleeves that reach to knee level. A lucky animal is weaved onto the skirt, inspired by a dream the client had.

char_497_ctable_nian#9.name: Illumination That of Daylights
char_497_ctable_nian#9.description: 0011 New Arrivals/Illumination That of Daylights. Made by Lungmen tailors. The gauze lining at the hem softens the lines, as does the matching white shawl.

char_473_mberry_nian#9.name: Reflection That of the Moons
char_473_mberry_nian#9.imgAlt: Mulberry's "Reflection That of the Moons" skin
char_473_mberry_nian#9.description: 0011 New Arrivals/Reflection That of the Moons. Made by Lungmen tailors, inspired by the waterscapes of Jiangqi, the delicate cuts and soft gauze represent the reflection of the lotus in water when the moon is out.

char_2013_cerber_whirlwind#2.name: Unfettered
char_2013_cerber_whirlwind#2.description: 0011 Tempest Series New Release/Unfettered. A set of children's clothes, Columbian in origin. Vulcan's reward to Ceobe for being a good girl.

char_243_waaifu_whirlwind#2.name: Wild Flower of Street
char_243_waaifu_whirlwind#2.imgAlt: Waai Fu's "Wild Flower of Street" skin
char_243_waaifu_whirlwind#2.description: 0011 Tempest Series New Release/Wild Flower of Street. A custom Lungmen-style outfit, tight-fitting attire made entirely from aged leather. Rugged and good-looking at the same time.

char_347_jaksel_whirlwind#2.name: Take a Leap
char_347_jaksel_whirlwind#2.description: 0011 Tempest Series New Release/Take a Leap. Green jacket over a simple shirt, with a pair of jeans and protective pads. Very easy to move in, making it well-suited for the outdoors.

char_378_asbest_whirlwind#3.name: Glen Sonata
char_378_asbest_whirlwind#3.description: 0011 Tempest Series New Release/Glen Sonata. Limited-edition padded jacket with leather bottoms and artisan accessories. SOLD OUT: STAY TUNED FOR ANNOUNCEMENTS ABOUT RESTOCKING.

char_366_acdrop_whirlwind#4.name: 'Afternoon Teatime'
char_366_acdrop_whirlwind#4.description: 0011 Tempest Series New Arrivals/'Afternoon Teatime'. A cozy, snug-fitting exercise wardrobe paired with a vivid jacket, ensuring the customer will be the center of attention wherever they go.

char_430_fartth_whirlwind#5.name: Hear the Wind Sing
char_430_fartth_whirlwind#5.description: 0011 Tempest Series/Hear the Wind Sing. New concept based on the theme of Wind, a collaborative work between multiple designers. The ever-present floating ribbons capture the shape of the wind.

char_4025_aprot2_whirlwind#5.name: The Fruition
char_4025_aprot2_whirlwind#5.description: 0011 Tempest Series/The Fruition. Classic black and white, with just a touch of color. No need for complex ornamentations; any flair belongs to the performer alone.

char_4071_peper_whirlwind#5.name: The Road to Here
char_4071_peper_whirlwind#5.description: 0011 Tempest Series/The Road to Here. Loose-fitting coat that can envelop a young girl. The waterproof fabric makes it suitable for a rainy day.

char_131_flameb_whirlwind#6.name: One Blade
char_131_flameb_whirlwind#6.description: 0011 Tempest Series New Arrivals/One Blade. Form-fitting, cool, and breathable sportswear, for those patrolling the streets. In a fistfight, the flowing scarlet sleeves become a raging flame. The accompanying sword is most certainly not a prop.

char_147_shining_summer#1.name: Silent Night DN02
char_147_shining_summer#1.description: MARTHE [Coral Coast] Silent Night Series Swimming Suit Type 02. The material is light, soft, breathable and durable. The latest design that is as enchanting as it is elegant.

char_166_skfire_summer#1.name: Temperature Difference RT.RX01
char_166_skfire_summer#1.description: MARTHE [Coral Coast] Temperature Difference Series Swimming Suit Type RX01. Attached with various accessories for convenient use. The special material is fire and cold-proof and suitable for activities in a variety of waters.

char_290_vigna_summer#1.name: Casual Vacation HD01
char_290_vigna_summer#1.description: MARTHE [Coral Coast] Casual Vacation Series HD01. Comfortable, relaxed, breathable, and lightweight. Allows you to enjoy a perfect beach experience in absolute relaxation.

char_212_ansel_summer#1.name: Casual Vacation HDm06
char_212_ansel_summer#1.description: MARTHE [Coral Coast] Casual Vacation Series HDm06 for men. Comfortable, relaxed, breathable, and lightweight. Allows you to enjoy a perfect beach experience in absolute relaxation. Critically acclaimed outfit for men, on sale now.

char_134_ifrit_summer#1.name: Sunburn SS.SP
char_134_ifrit_summer#1.description: MARTHE [Coral Coast] Sunburn Series Swimming Suit Type SP. Special Rhine Lab Collaboration Type. To meet Rhine Lab's specifications, this outfit is both comfortable and possesses heat-resistant properties.

char_101_sora_summer#1.name: Summer Flowers FA361
char_101_sora_summer#1.description: MARTHE [Coral Coast] Summer Flowers Series FA361. Brings out a girl's figure and physique using all-natural materials. Pursue this summer's hottest trend.

char_199_yak_summer#1.description: MARTHE [Coral Coast] Beach Guard Series Swimming Suit Launch Type 001. Made with materials that are both durable and comfortable, this outfit ensures high performance in a variety of different conditions.

char_286_cast3_summer#1.name: SUM019.ver
char_286_cast3_summer#1.description: MARTHE [Coral Coast] Raythean Style SUMMER Special Painting. Equipped with heat-proof coating, the latest sand wheels, and reinforced engineering. It is specially modified for operations on the beach.

char_263_skadi_summer#3.name: Waverider WR04
char_263_skadi_summer#3.description: MARTHE [Coral Coast] Waverider Series WR04. This swimsuit tailor-made for Ægir beachgoers allows inhabitants of the sea to look dazzling on the sand.

char_145_prove_summer#3.description: MARTHE [Coral Coast] Casual Vacation Series HD08. Comfortable, relaxed, breathable, and lightweight. Allows you to enjoy a perfect beach experience in absolute relaxation.

char_172_svrash_summer#4.description: MARTHE [Coral Coast] Seeker Series Swimming Suit SKm01. The material is light, breathable and exquisite. It's been tailored to meet the needs of those inventive elites.

char_1023_ghost2_boc#6.description: Bloodline of Combat Collection/Born as One. An engraving leaves a shadow, like two sides of a coin, or the cycle of day and night. When both are aware of their dual nature, Laurentina possesses a soul most complete, like unto the twin moons.

char_1013_chen2_boc#6.name: Ten Thousand Mountains
char_1013_chen2_boc#6.imgAlt: Ch'en the Holungday's "Ten Thousand Mountains" skin
char_1013_chen2_boc#6.description: Bloodline of Combat Collection/Ten Thousand Mountains. Ch'en Hui-chieh entered the capital on a starry night, and left before sunrise after settling matters. She bid farewell to old friends and took a sampan down the river, the lamp on the prow crashing through the fog and night.

char_4046_ebnhlz_boc#6.name: Eine Variation
char_4046_ebnhlz_boc#6.description: Bloodline of Combat Collection/Eine Variation. A traditional-style gown worn by every Graf Urtica, now draped over Ebenholz's shoulders. Orders apathetically seep from the tip of the staff, piercing through the sparse ensemble of nobles.

char_278_orchid_boc#6.name: Twines of Time
char_278_orchid_boc#6.description: Bloodline of Combat Collection/Twines of Time. Orchid finally completed her design after several torturous nights. She stroked the delicate stitches on it, quietly praying for life.

char_4000_jnight_boc#7.name: Tournament Fantasy Retrofit Kit
char_4000_jnight_boc#7.description: Bloodline of Combat Collection/Tournament Fantasy Retrofit Kit. The General Chamber of Commerce had no idea the newest wave of protests would arise from a most unremarkable robot's tournament retrofit labelled as a 'drone.'

char_103_angel_kfc#1.name: City Rider
char_103_angel_kfc#1.description: Rhodes Kitchen Collection/City Rider. Designed by Exusiai herself, 'I didn't think too much about the design, actually. I just made something that I'd like to wear.'

char_134_ifrit_kfc#1.name: Children's Party
char_134_ifrit_kfc#1.description: Rhodes Kitchen Collection/Children's Party. Designed by Silence. Made with special materials from Rhine Lab, it offers a completely unnecessary amount of protection.

char_201_moeshd_kfc#1.description: Rhodes Kitchen Collection/Seven in the Morning. Designed by Croissant. Actually just recycled Exusiai's design because it's cheaper to do it that way.

char_173_slchan_wwf#1.name: Highlands Visitor
char_173_slchan_wwf#1.description: WWF Collaborative Series/Highlands Visitor. Using synthetic materials to capture the inspiration of the great outdoors, this outfit is capable of adapting to adverse environments and protects experienced explorers as they visit every corner of Terra.

char_202_demkni_boc#1.name: Stronghold
char_202_demkni_boc#1.description: Bloodline of Combat Collection/Stronghold. An outfit worn by Saria during the confrontation between the General Jurisdiction and the Research Branch. Though her surroundings crumbled under the onslaught of Arts colliding, her conviction never wavered, like the land itself.

char_291_aglina_boc#1.name: Distinguished Visitor
char_291_aglina_boc#1.description: Bloodline of Combat Collection/Distinguished Visitor. The outfit worn by Angelina while she was stationed at the 2nd Final Defense Front. The substance of reality slowly flows between her fingers and her tools.

char_140_whitew_boc#1.name: Refined Horrormare
char_140_whitew_boc#1.description: Bloodline of Combat Collection/Refined Horrormare. The outfit Lappland wore at the Laterano Apostolic Knights' Funeral Memorial Hall. Collect the debts, and pay the price.

char_279_excu_boc#1.name: Titleless Code
char_279_excu_boc#1.description: Bloodline of Combat Collection/Titleless Code. The outfit worn by Executor when tracking important charges for the Laterano Notarial Hall. Though one's identity may change over the years, what the heart desires does not.

char_367_swllow_boc#1.name: Homecoming
char_367_swllow_boc#1.description: Bloodline of Combat Collection/Homecoming. The outfit worn by Operator GreyThroat while participating in a rescue operation for the Infected within the Catastrophe zone of Sugar City. Disregarding protection or camouflage, upon this outfit is etched the will to protect the next person, and save another life.

char_283_midn_boc#1.name: Seventh Night's Awakened
char_283_midn_boc#1.description: Bloodline of Combat Collection/Seventh Night's Awakened. An outfit worn by Midnight during the promotional video of an annihilation operation. Though it was undeniably effective, everyone agreed that it was a bit over-the-top.

char_122_beagle_boc#1.name: Dreadnaught
char_122_beagle_boc#1.description: Bloodline of Combat Collection/Dreadnaught. The attire worn by the elite operator, Beagle, when serving as rearguard during the Great March of Bolívar. This is her final test.

char_188_helage_boc#2.name: Octopath Illusion
char_188_helage_boc#2.description: Bloodline of Combat Collection/Octopath Illusion. Hellagur's clothing during his time as vanguard commander in the Bloodpeak Campaign. If he weren't an enemy, if he could have served Ursus... Even if no such possibility existed.

char_118_yuki_boc#2.name: Wind of Breaking Blade
char_118_yuki_boc#2.description: Bloodline of Combat Collection/Wind of Breaking Blade. Shirayuki's combat attire in her confrontation with Samuraitaisho serving the North, during the Northern and Southern Courts Battle of Echigo. The head orders: sight enemy, see blood.

char_264_f12yin_boc#3.name: Dark Cloud
char_264_f12yin_boc#3.description: Bloodline of Combat Collection/Dark Cloud. Mountain's attire at his parents' funeral. Though he personally slew his own enemy, there is no hint of joy in his heart. There are still things he needs to do.

char_416_zumama_boc#3.name: Forgemaster
char_416_zumama_boc#3.description: Bloodline of Combat Collection/Forgemaster. Rhodes Island Engineering Chief Eunectes's outfit while refitting an experimental-model Raging Ironhide. Every point worked on all by herself, everyone saying she's much more reliable than Closure. Closure fiercely rolling her eyes.

char_294_ayer_boc#3.name: Tested One
char_294_ayer_boc#3.description: Bloodline of Combat Collection/Tested One. Ayerscarpe's attire while upgrading the Rim Billiton Weapon Distribution Center weapons system. He needs to infiltrate a Catastrophe area together with his friends, and heist an important piece of data back before the Columbians.

char_415_flint_boc#3.name: Gorgeous Flower
char_415_flint_boc#3.description: Bloodline of Combat Collection/Gorgeous Flower. Flint's attire when she set out on a lone journey, a 'Catastrophe Messenger' by her own declaration. Before, her fists only knew Acahualla and Rhodes Island. Now, it's Terra's turn.

char_284_spot_boc#3.name: Professional
char_284_spot_boc#3.description: Bloodline of Combat Collection/Professional. The outfit Spot wore for an Annihilation mission promo. It might've been effective, but all Spot's thinking about is what cartoons are on tonight.

char_248_mgllan_kitchen#1.name: Shaved-Ice Memories
char_248_mgllan_kitchen#1.description: Rhodes Kitchen Collection/Shaved-Ice Memories. The work outfit worn by Magallan to make shaved ice during the food festival combines traditions of Higashi with characteristics of Rhine Labs. Breathable, well-insulated, and easy to move in, this outfit allows Magallan to fully devote herself to her work, even if in a shaved-ice shop.

char_195_glassb_kitchen#1.name: Bibliosmia
char_195_glassb_kitchen#1.description: Rhodes Kitchen Collection/Bibliosmia. After being re-coordinated to reflect the national outfits of the people of Ursus, Istina wore this outfit to promote traditional cuisine at the food festival. Underneath the plain materials are countless intricate details, and only those who deem themselves wise come to seek answers.

char_137_brownb_kitchen#1.name: Honey Pilferer
char_137_brownb_kitchen#1.description: Rhodes Kitchen Collection/Honey Pilferer. Beehunter's sleepwear. Fluffy, soft, comfortable, tight-fitting, and easy to wash, this outfit is suitable for both home use and as sleepwear. What nobody expected is that Beehunter would head straight to the food festival.

token_10007_phatom_twin_ghost#1.name: Dream Within a Dreammare
token_10007_phatom_twin_ghost#1.imgAlt: Phantom in the Mirror's "Dream Within a Dreammare" skin

char_250_phatom_ghost#1.name: Dream Within a Dreammare
char_250_phatom_ghost#1.description: Clothes of Phantom's, the attire he sported while staffing the 'Dreambind Castle' event. The dance as cloth, the song as silk, the threading through emotion, the tailoring by fabrication, the weave of obliteration and howling madness, it all culminates in this majestic yet skin-crawling ensemble.

char_242_otter_ghost#1.name: Visionblazer in the Courtyard
char_242_otter_ghost#1.description: Multimedia Escape Experience 'Dreambind Castle' Visitor's Prepared Outfit/Visionblazer in the Courtyard. The outfit Mayer wore for the code-cracking event 'Courtyard Tidings.' Mayer loved all the puzzles her coworkers designed, and took to making short work of them.

char_326_glacus_ghost#1.name: Exterminator in the Square
char_326_glacus_ghost#1.description: Multimedia Escape Experience 'Dreambind Castle' Visitor's Prepared Outfit/Exterminator in the Square. The outfit Glaucus wore for the photoshoot event 'Cyclonic Square.' Prior to the photographer clicking the shutter, Glaucus needed to nail down her pose.

char_277_sqrrel_ghost#1.name: Cleansweeper in the Castle
char_277_sqrrel_ghost#1.description: Multimedia Escape Experience 'Dreambind Castle' Visitor's Prepared Outfit/Cleansweeper in the Castle. The outfit Shaw wore for the investigation event 'Trails in the Castle.' While Shaw trawls the castle scenery, she's prepared to fend off unexpected guests at any time.

char_222_bpipe_race#1.name: Queen, No.1
char_222_bpipe_race#1.description: Whistlewind Series Race Queen Core Line/Queen, No.1. In full race queen form, sporting a Raythean-sponsored Piledriver Spear, Bagpipe carries herself tall and brings the spectators' cheers non-stop.

char_456_ash_rainbow6#1.name: Ranger
char_456_ash_rainbow6#1.description: Rainbow Six Collab Series/Ranger. This outfit, hand-picked by Ash herself, emphasizes both disguisability and sportiness. A specially-made hat conceals Ash's identity, facilitating intelligence-gathering and related work.

char_459_tachak_rainbow6#1.name: Lord
char_459_tachak_rainbow6#1.description: Rainbow Six Collab Series/Lord. A set of tactical armor that consists of the helmet Tachanka picked from the Lord of Long Spring's collection and a modified set of standard issue battle armor. It has exceptional defensive capabilities, which is further topped off with an imposing appearance that can be seen from afar.

char_340_shwaz_striker#1.name: Skyline
char_340_shwaz_striker#1.description: Striker Series/Skyline. A product of Raythean Industries, geared for hypothetical city combat environs. Along with basic protection, the application of the latest in reflective paint allows specialist personnel to blend into the complex surroundings of the city.

char_107_liskam_striker#1.name: Overload
char_107_liskam_striker#1.description: Striker Series/Overload. A product of Raythean Industries, a combat outfit fully tailored to exceptional specialist personnel. Offers reliable defense in all environments, further supports the Operator's own Originium Arts.

char_112_siege_striker#2.name: City Destroyer
char_112_siege_striker#2.description: Striker Series/City Destroyer. A product of Raythean Industries, this defensive gear is designed for robust combat, with additional high-density shock-absorbent elements present in the lining that answer the impact of attacks, while simultaneously tailored in parts to ensure high flexibility.

char_155_tiger_striker#2.name: Valiant General
char_155_tiger_striker#2.description: Striker Series/Valiant General. A product of Raythean Industries, this traditional Victorian formal attire has been reworked with upgraded materials across the board, alongside a lining imbued with the latest in structured textiles, providing effective protection against sharp instruments.

char_149_scave_striker#2.name: Survive
char_149_scave_striker#2.description: Striker Series/Survive. A product of Raythean Industries, adopting the latest in adaptive clothing material, paired with an all-encompassing tailoring that tightly hugs the skin, ensuring operators' survival under the most extreme circumstances.

char_017_huang_as#1.name: Burst Feline
char_017_huang_as#1.description: Ambience Synesthesia Tailor-Provided/Burst Feline. Stage clothing picked by drummer Blaze herself. There might not be much material, but it's breathable, sweat-absorbent and flame-resistant, ensuring no outfit malfunctions will affect Blaze's performance.

char_198_blackd_as#1.name: Speechless Sound
char_198_blackd_as#1.description: Ambience Synesthesia Tailor-Provided/Speechless Sound. Stage clothing picked by bassist Courier himself. People think of Kjerag's men as steadfast and untalkative, but Courier's ready with his bass to change their perception.

char_290_vigna_as#1.name: Black Wave
char_290_vigna_as#1.description: Ambience Synesthesia Tailor-Provided/Black Wave. Stage clothing picked by guitarist Vigna herself. The outfit in whole has been languishing in Vigna's wardrobe for a while, and she's always wanted to give it a stage showing. The chance has now arrived.

char_311_mudrok_ambienceSynesthesia#2.name: Obsidian
char_311_mudrok_ambienceSynesthesia#2.description: Ambience Synesthesia Tailor-Provided/Obsidian. Mudrock's work outfit. Mudrock made rounds between every facility at the venue, ensuring the performance would go without a hitch. Though working behind the scenes, she nevertheless opted for a disguise of sorts so as not to disturb the audience.

char_486_takila_ambienceSynesthesia#2.name: Cardwinner
char_486_takila_ambienceSynesthesia#2.description: Ambience Synesthesia Tailor-Provided/Cardwinner. Tequila's formal stage outfit. Qualified hosts heat up the audience; excellent hosts strive to eliminate any errant possibility.

char_261_sddrag_ambienceSynesthesia#2.name: Emerald Holiday
char_261_sddrag_ambienceSynesthesia#2.description: Ambience Synesthesia Tailor-Provided/Emerald Holiday. Reed's plain outfit during downtime. Lyrics have limits, and manuscripts have deadlines, but all that's still far, far away. They're no worry; in the comfort of the afternoon sun, finishing your glass of juice comes first.

char_4042_lumen_ambienceSynesthesia#3.name: Golden Dream
char_4042_lumen_ambienceSynesthesia#3.description: Ambience Synesthesia Tailor-Provided/Golden Dream. Lumen's casual leisure wear, tailored for elegance from lightweight materials. The sea mist has lifted, and you can now see the lighthouse without binoculars.

char_4009_irene_ambienceSynesthesia#3.name: Voyage of Feathers
char_4009_irene_ambienceSynesthesia#3.description: Ambience Synesthesia Tailor-Provided/Voyage of Feathers. Irene's work outfit. Placed in charge of the props, she sets them in place, as a flock of fowlbeasts circles higher into the sky, ships sailing into the distant horizon.

token_10018_robrta_mach_ambienceSynesthe.name: Granter of Colors
token_10018_robrta_mach_ambienceSynesthe.imgAlt: Full Auto Modeler's "Granter of Colors" skin

char_484_robrta_ambienceSynesthesia#3.name: Granter of Colors
char_484_robrta_ambienceSynesthesia#3.description: Ambience Synesthesia Tailor-Provided/Granter of Colors. Roberta's work outfit. With the other operators' help and encouragement, Roberta finally found the time to design a look for herself as well.

char_293_thorns_it#1.name: Cómodo
char_293_thorns_it#1.description: I.T Brand UNDER GARDEN Collab Outfit/Cómodo. A black and white base, the third color freely selectable. A casual design, a multi-modular composition for balanced action/everyday effect.

char_350_surtr_it#1.name: Liberté//Échec
char_350_surtr_it#1.description: I.T Brand UNDER GARDEN Collab Outfit/Liberté//Échec. A black and red base. A non-integrated design, with multiple accessories to select, the complete effect taking on personalized preferences.

char_115_headbr_it#1.name: Ursus IO79
char_115_headbr_it#1.description: I.T Brand UNDER GARDEN Collab Outfit/Ursus IO79. A black and red base. A compact design, drawing from casual accessories to give a boost to color variety, bringing about a brand new fashion experience.

char_358_lisa_lxh#1.name: Spring Praise
char_358_lisa_lxh#1.description: The Legend of Luo Xiaohei Collaborative Series/Spring Praise. Rustic apparel commonly seen in Terra's central regions. Simple and easygoing, hardy against wear and dirt. Best suited to journeys, outings, and other such daily activities.

char_4040_rockr_lxh#1.name: Before Singing
char_4040_rockr_lxh#1.description: The Legend of Luo Xiaohei Collaborative Series/Before Singing. Glossy texturing and a bright palette make for materials that shout energy, while contour-hugging innerwear pairs with a loose-fit jacket to provide both comfort and chic.

char_4077_palico_mh#1.name: Fly Into the Street
char_4077_palico_mh#1.imgAlt: Terra Research Commission's "Fly Into the Street" skin
char_4077_palico_mh#1.description: Monster Hunter Collaborative Series/Fly Into the Street. The Felynes are amped with excitement for getting some Terra-style fresh fits on, and spray paint-filled cans especially pique their curiosity. Noir Corne senses something big and bad's about to go down.

char_332_archet_shining#1.name: Publicity Strategy
char_332_archet_shining#1.description: Monster Siren Records Idol Project 'Shining Steps' Promotional Costume/Publicity Strategy. The cloistered idol Hildegard, appearing with the sponsorship from MountainDash Logistics, sings the praises of Landen Monstery in a modern, fashionable way.

char_274_astesi_shining#1.name: Frlibe on the Palace
char_274_astesi_shining#1.description: Monster Siren Records Idol Project 'Shining Steps' Promotional Costume/Frlibe on the Palace. Astesia joins the project at her own expense, looking to interpret the stories written in the sky in a popular and easily accessible way.

char_440_pinecn_shining#1.name: Sing a Song
char_440_pinecn_shining#1.description: Monster Siren Records Idol Project 'Shining Steps' Promotional Costume/Sing a Song. After passing her audition, Pinecone took to the stage with no especially strong desire to be an idol. She just wants to sing.

char_159_peacok_game#1.name: Your Superconvicting Friend
char_159_peacok_game#1.description: Achievement Star Collection/Your Superconvicting Friend. A complimentary outfit that came with the luxury limited edition of a retro arcade machine. Loose and relaxed with a classic palette, this fit will both flaunt your gamer status and accompany you on your daily outings.

char_420_flamtl_game#2.name: Sport For All
char_420_flamtl_game#2.description: Achievement Star Collection/Sport For All. Sporty outfit worn by Flametail when playing VR games. The limited space is made even more cramped by the gaming equipment, but she has a great time nonetheless.

char_346_aosta_game#2.name: Light Gun Adjuster
char_346_aosta_game#2.description: Achievement Star Collection/Light Gun Adjuster. The outfit Aosta wore while working for the Family, paired with tactical equipment. He also likes to wear it when testing light guns at Rhodes Island.

char_478_kirara_game#2.name: Trendsetting Player
char_478_kirara_game#2.description: Achievement Star Collection/Trendsetting Player. A gift from the devs, thrown in when Kirara bought a complete set of gaming equipment. Customized just for her, a loose and comfortable outfit for around the home.

char_2023_ling_ncg#1.name: Towering is Cliff of Nostalgia
char_2023_ling_ncg#1.imgAlt: Ling's "Towering is Cliff of Nostalgia" skin
char_2023_ling_ncg#1.description: Brand Collaborative Series/Towering is Cliff of Nostalgia. Stylish and classic. The wind brushes the cliffs for a thousand years, a thousand li, brushing against the wanderer's robes, brushing into dream.

char_4082_qiubai_ncg#1.name: Wine-flushed is Woods of Rime
char_4082_qiubai_ncg#1.imgAlt: Qiubai's "Wine-flushed is Woods of Rime" skin
char_4082_qiubai_ncg#1.description: Brand Collaborative Series/Wine-flushed is Woods of Rime. Wind-proof and wear-resistant with a clean, slim fit that's easy to move in. Inspired by the northwest poplar forests.

char_106_franka_ncg#1.name: Rainforest, Me, Rainbow
char_106_franka_ncg#1.description: Brand Collaborative Series/Rainforest, Me, Rainbow. The waterproof, breathable fabric comes in handy for rainforest work. Lightweight, wear-resistant, and protects from the sun. Tail attachment optional.

char_4019_ncdeer_ncdeer#1.name: A Silvern Caress On the Flow of Time
char_4019_ncdeer_ncdeer#1.imgAlt: Nine-Colored Deer's "A Silvern Caress On the Flow of Time" skin
char_4019_ncdeer_ncdeer#1.description: 'Nine-Colored Deer' Collaborative Series/A Silvern Caress On the Flow of Time. Crossing the golden sands yet leaving nary a trace, time passes quietly along with the moon's shadow. Nine-Colored Deer meticulously counts the tracks left behind by the passing years, and thus the full moon pauses, seeking one to converse with.

char_4078_bdhkgt_yun#2.name: Away From Dust
char_4078_bdhkgt_yun#2.description: 0011 Yun Series New Arrivals/Away From Dust. Made by expert Yanese tailors, the stylish, narrow-sleeved robe is cool and comfortable. Jieyun wore it while visiting Yan's rivers and lakes.

char_4014_lunacu_yun#1.name: Clouds Float Like Ideas of Art
char_4014_lunacu_yun#1.imgAlt: Lunacub's "Clouds Float Like Ideas of Art" skin
char_4014_lunacu_yun#1.description: 0011 Yun Series/Clouds Float Like Ideas of Art. Presented by the finest Yanese artisans, combining classic style with trendy spirit.

char_4048_doroth_witch#4.name: Hand of Destiny
char_4048_doroth_witch#4.description: Witch Feast Role-Playing Script 'Dominions & Dogma' Custom Line/Hand of Destiny. This player shall be the will of the realm behind the story. She is neither a wicked god, nor a righteous spirit. All she does is let the players roll the dice.

char_300_phenxi_witch#4.name: Divine Oath
char_300_phenxi_witch#4.description: Witch Feast Role-Playing Script 'Dominions & Dogma' Custom Line/Divine Oath. This player shall be the apostolic knight who takes charge in times of crisis. She is the crimson fury spilling forth from the Holy Spirit's palm, bearing the eternal burden of seeking the land of salvation.

char_492_quercu_witch#4.name: The Bard's Tale
char_492_quercu_witch#4.description: Witch Feast Role-Playing Script 'Dominions & Dogma' Custom Line/The Bard's Tale. This player shall be the one singing ballads for the heroes of old, livening up the tavern with her ditties. Come, listen close, who stole the melody that wends through the shadow-flickering breeze?

char_436_whispr_witch#4.name: Priory of Abyss
char_436_whispr_witch#4.description: Witch Feast Role-Playing Script 'Dominions & Dogma' Custom Line/Priory of Abyss. This player shall be the sister in black, who has saved countless adventurers' lives. The people never ask who forgets the traumas of their mundane lives for them.

char_1028_texas2_iteration#1.name: Wingbreaker
char_1028_texas2_iteration#1.description: Iteration Provident Series/Wingbreaker. Texas the Omertosa's iteration from decision point F/3019226. The hunter shot down the great demon Vermithrax, but was betrayed by the Lone Wolf Emperor and banished to the barrens.

char_297_hamoni_unveiling#1.name: Decoration
char_297_hamoni_unveiling#1.description: Unveiling of Devotion Series New Arrivals/Decoration. A cute dress Harmonie rarely wears. With its adjustable fit and flexible materials, it can accentuate the body's natural curves better than any other. The accessories are all from her beloved private collection.

char_271_spikes_unveiling#1.name: Dangerous Invitation
char_271_spikes_unveiling#1.description: Unveiling of Devotion Series New Arrivals/Dangerous Invitation. A graceful custom-made suit just for Arene. The stiff material is painstakingly cut to fit his youthful figure. He also personally selected the accompanying perfume.

char_1001_amiya2_2.name: Elite 2
char_1001_amiya2_2.description: Black particles have formed her vambrace. People with the knowledge may recognize it as one part of an ancient king's armor.
